According to the latest release of Covid-19 statistics, by the Mpumalanga Department of Health, Steve Tshwete is currently standing at 382 positive cases and 121 recoveries. eMalahleni remains the district with the highest number of infections within the province and has leapt to 1064. The Govan Mbeki district has 494 and the City of Mbombela 477. The total number of positive cases for the Mpumalanga Province is 3596.